<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Reinstatement - Smile Sync</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f0f8ff;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
      }
      .notification-container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 500px;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #155724;
        background-color: #d4edda;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 26px;
      }
      .important-note {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #0c5460;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      p {
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .info {
        color: #6c757d;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        background-color: #28a745;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #218838;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #888;
      }
      .success-icon {
        font-size: 50px;
        color: #28a745;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      ul {
        text-align: left;
        color: #555;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="notification-container">
      <div class="success-icon">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="64"
          height="64"
          fill="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 16 16"
        >
          <path
            d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0zm-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"
          />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1>Account Reinstatement Notice</h1>
      <p>Hello <%= userName %>,</p>
      <p>
        We're pleased to inform you that your Smile Sync account has been
        reinstated after careful review.
      </p>

      <div class="important-note">
        Your full account access has been restored!
      </div>

      <p class="info">
        Our team has completed the review process and determined that your
        account can be restored. We appreciate your patience and understanding
        during this process.
      </p>

      <p>With this reinstatement:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>You can now log in to your account normally</li>
        <li>All account features have been restored</li>
        <li>You may resume using our services</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        We welcome you back to Smile Sync and encourage you to review our
        <a href="https://www.smilesync.com/terms" style="color: #28a745"
          >Terms of Service</a
        >
        to ensure continued positive experience for all users.
      </p>

      <a href="https://www.smilesync.com/login" class="btn"
        >Login to Your Account</a
      >

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Welcome back,</p>
        <p>The Smile Sync Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
